[title]
Check if guest's clock tick policy is set appropriately for rtc and pit timer.

[description]

Check if rtc timer is available and if so, check if tickpolicy is catchup.
Check if pit timer is availalbe and if so, check if tickpolicy is delay.

This is more relevant and important for Windows guest and guests running either  RHEL 5.4 and SLES10 SP4 or lower versions.
